items.title: Australia Accuses Iran of Directing Antisemitic Arson Attacks
items.description: The government expelled Iran’s diplomats, saying the country was behind the attacks on a Melbourne synagogue and a Sydney restaurant last year.

items.title: Police Officers Descend on Australian Town After Reports of Fatal Shooting
items.description: The national broadcaster reported that at least two police officers had been killed in a rural town north of Melbourne. The police declined to comment...
